2. Unzip it into the plugins folder (one level depth)
    ```
    cd ~/Downloads    # probably
    
    # release v>1.0
    unzip fire2am.zip
    mv fire2am/fire2am ~/.local/share/QGIS/QGIS3/profiles/default/python/plugins/
    
